
Overview of noun bait

The noun bait has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (1) bait, come-on, hook, lure, sweetener -- (anything that serves as an enticement)
2. bait, decoy, lure -- (something used to lure fish or other animals into danger so they can be trapped or killed)

